e needs and manage impending debt obligations.\n\n(What's moving Sensex and Nifty Track latest market news, stock tips, Budget 2025, Share Market on Budget 2025 and expert advice, on ETMarkets. Also, ETMarkets.com is now on Telegram. For fastest news alerts on financial markets, investment strateg", "citation": "Amazon aims to raise $25 billion from bond sale, Bloomberg News reports \u2014 ET Markets, 2026-07-07. https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/stocks/news/amazon-aims-to-raise-25-billion-from-bond-sale-bloomberg-news-reports/articleshow/132242087.cms"}, {"title": "Global Market: Britain's bond market poses early fiscal test for Andy Burnham", "feed": "ET Markets", "ts": "2026-07-07T03:39:01+00:00", "url": "https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/us-stocks/news/global-market-britains-bond-market-poses-early-fiscal-test-for-andy-burnham/articleshow/132235449.cms", "status": "ok", "excerpt": "Britain's government bond market is expected to be a key test for Andy Burnham's economic credibility as investors scrutinise his commitment to fiscal discipline amid mounting spending pressures. While easing bond yields have offered some relief, analysts say persistent inflation risks and rising debt servicing costs will keep markets focused on the UK's fiscal outlook.\n\n(What's moving Sensex and Nifty Track latest market news, stock tips, Budget 2025, Share Market on Budget 2025 and expert advice, on ETMarkets. Also, ETMarkets.com is now on Telegram. For fastest news alerts on financial markets, investment strategies and stocks alerts, subscribe to our Telegram feeds .)\n\nSubscribe to ET Pri", "citation": "Global Market: Britain's bond market poses early fiscal test for Andy Burnham \u2014 ET Markets, 2026-07-07. https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/us-stocks/news/global-market-britains-bond-market-poses-early-fiscal-test-for-andy-burnham/articleshow/132235449.cms"}], "primary_sources": [{"series": "dyn_bond", "name": "Yahoo \u00b7 BOND", "url": "http